# Implementation Plan - Scout Dashboard

## Goal
Create a beautiful, user-friendly web interface for the sales team to view lead dossiers and export data, replacing the raw Google Sheet view.

## Technology
- **Framework:** Streamlit (Python) - Fast to build, good for data apps.
- **Data Source:** Google Sheets ("Scout Leads").
- **Styling:** Custom CSS to make it look "premium" and not like a default Streamlit app.

